subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Steady rain washed out matches at the Fed Cup quarterfinal between Germany and the United States in San Diego, forcing organizers to try again Monday. The best-of-five series was tied, 1-1. The winner will move on to face defending champion Russia, which reached the semifinals by beating Israel. China and Spain also reached the semifinals.
